node.text:
🙌🏼 Shomaliha dasta bala! You know I love surprising you but today I just have to give you a hint. Shooting an episode of @bereezobepaz and it’s allllll about the Rashtis. Just wait until you see who is in my kitchen today. Airing on @voafarsi late October. It’s a surprise. 
For my non-Persian friends. My mom is from a part of Iran called Rasht. My name Shally means a grain of rice from the rice fields of Shalizar found in that area 🌾🌾🌾
They are the kindest, sweetest and most loving and bahal people. Not to mention they cook some of my my FAVORITE foods on this planet. Are you ready? 
TI JANEH GHORBAN 💋
Love your song @darvishmasoud 💜
یه قسمت دیگه بریز و بپز رو امروز داریم فیلم میگریم. نمی‌‌تونم بهتون بگم اینجا چه خبره ولی فقط بگم که پرچم رشت‌یا بالاست ❤️🌾

It’s really happening! We are now shooting the episodes for @bereezobepaz airing on @voafarsi starting late October. Production crew setting up next scene so I have a break to show you what’s happening behind the scenes 🎥 
خیلی خوشحال هستم که فیلمبرداری برنامه بریز و بپز رو شروع کردیم که به زودی از صدای آمریکا پخش خواهد شد، بچه های گروه فیلمبرداری دارند حاضر می‌شوند برای صحنه های دیگه منم از فرصت استفاده کردم تا بهتون نشون بدم اینجا چه خبره.

I was born and raised in California. I have never lived in Iran and the last time I visited I was only 4 years old. But my love for the culture and where I come from runs through my veins. 
You often see me cooking, dancing and speaking in Persian as I fight to keep my
Culture alive for my kids and the generation who may not know the Iran our parents know. And now I found a way to bring our cultures even closer together. Through food, dance, laughter and LOVE we are excited to announce the coming of a new cooking show
 ✨BEREEZ-O-BEPAZ ba Shally✨
airing on Voice of America beginning late October. 
This kitchen is for dancing. And from it we create LOVE that we are packaging up and sending to you soon! 💜
@voafarsi @samanism so so excited! Let the magic begin! 
✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨
من توی کالیفرنیا به دنیا اومدم و همینجا بزرگ شدم و هیچوقت توی ایران زندگی نکردم، آخرین باری که ایران بودم ۴ سالم بود. ولی عاشق ایران ‌و فرهنگ ایران هستم و قلبم برای جایی که ازش اومدم میزنه. 
همه سعی‌ام رو کردم که با رقص، آشپزی و حرف زدن فرهنگ ایران رو برای بچه‌هام و کسانی که شاید کمتر با فرهنگ ایران آشنایی دارن نشون بدم و زنده نگه‌اش دارم. 
 آشپزی، رقص، شادی و خنده بهانه‌ای هست که در این روزهای سخت، عشق رو به خونه‌های شما بیاریم. 
“ بریز و بپز با شالی”
اواسط پاییز در کانال صدای آمریکا. 
شما هم میهمان آشپزخانه من باشید. 
@voafarsi @samanism
بزن و بریم
#voapersian #persian #bereezobepaz #shallyzomorodi

If you have been with me for awhile then you know I have shared my stories of being bullied when I was a child. Even today online I am still pushed around by people who want to humiliate and intimidate me. It is painful. But I am also grateful for having gone through these challenges because now stronger than ever I can share my story with others with the hopes to stop bullying. @drshaheem YOU ARE A GEM 💎 thank you for knowledge and guidance as we navigate through life. You have done so much work in the arena of anti-bullying and I am grateful for your support. Parents. I hope you find a moment to listen to her and this session. It will change your children’s lives. 
🦋 our pick-up event for today the book is now FULL. You can pre- order the book and doll on my website www.SHALLZ..com
So grateful for your love
And support

A few years ago after I decided to write a book I had the idea to find the illustrator through a search on social media. I received hundreds and hundreds of emails. Having a hard time picking someone I mentioned to my mom I was struggling and wish I could give everyone a chance. And that’s when everything changed. She told me I have a cousin in Iran who is an incredible artist and could possibly do it. 
And she did. We haven’t sent each other in more than 4 decades. She is my family. My cousin. And now the illustrator of my first book. 
@azi.cake1 I LOVE YOU! Thank you for helping me make my dreams come true. I pray for the day I can hold you and squeeze you again. 
ASHEGETAM AZI jooooon! 🦋
Today is the final day to pre-order you book and pick it up at a special event in SOCAL. Order yours at www.SHALLZ.com

They are the kindest, sweetest and most loving and bahal people. Not to mention they cook some of my my FAVORITE foods on this planet. Are you ready? 
TI JANEH GHORBAN 💋

node.text: NEW - In this session of More than Mind Dr. Samineh Shaheem and I explore the psychological elements associated with living outside of your home culture. What happens to your cultural identity? Why do some people seem more adjusted than others? Does the host culture every become our new home? You can join the conversation! Leave your comments and questions below and Dr. Shaheem will address a few of them. And if you see a moment in this session or any of our More than Mind sessions that resonates with you - record it. Post it on your stories and tag @drshaheem - and two of those people will receive a copy of Dr. Shaheem's book 'The Karma Hotel.' #morethanmind #mentalhealth #homesick #adaptation
